Package com.github.dm.jrt.channel

Utility classes handling routine channels.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ChannelsBuilder<TYPE>
    Interface defining a generic configurable builder of channels.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractBuilder<TYPE>
    Abstract base builder implementation.
    ByteChannel
    Utility class focused on the optimization of the transfer of byte chunks through routine channels.
    ByteChannel.BufferInputStream
    Input stream used to read the data contained in a buffer instance.
    ByteChannel.BufferOutputStream
    Output stream used to write data into the buffer channel.
    Channels
    Utility class for handling routine channels.
    The class provides several methods to split and merge channels together, making also possible to transfer data in multiple sub-channels, each one identified by a specific index.
    Selectable<DATA>
    Data class storing information about the origin of the data.
